name: Toshiba Dynabook Satellite
description: The Toshiba Dynabook Satellite Pro C40-G-109 Celeron 5205U 14" HD Laptop is powered by the Intel Celeron 5205U processor (2M Cache, 1.90 GHz) including UHD graphics, 4GB DDR4 3200MHz RAM, and 128GB M.2 SATA SSD. The Toshiba Dynabook Satellite Pro C40-G-109 is equipped with 802.11ac Wi-Fi, Bluetooth, and Gigabit-LAN. The laptop comes with a full-size HDMI port makes big-screen presentations easy, and a microSD card reader lets you access portable storage whenever you need to.
